{"word":"G4892 - συνέδριον - synédrion - soon-ed'-ree-on - Council","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συνέδριον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>synédrion"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>soon-ed'-ree-on"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Council"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"ஆலோசனைச்சங்கம், சங்கம் - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. any session or assembly of persons deliberating or adjudicating"},{"paragraph":"2. the Sanhedrin, the great council at Jerusalem"},{"paragraph":"3. the smaller tribunal or council"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Neuter of a presumed derivative of a compound of <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G1476 - ἑδραῖος - hedraîos - hed-rah'-yos/1476\">G1476</a>; a <i>joint session</i>, that is, (specifically) the Jewish <i>Sanhedrim</i>; by analogy a subordinate <i>tribunal:</i> - council."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}